<h3 class="endpoint">
    PUT /api/v1/courses/:course_id/tabs/:tab_id
  </h3>
<p>Home and Settings tabs are not manageable, and can't be hidden or moved</p>
<p>Returns a tab object</p>
<h4>Request Parameters:</h4>
